room_title: Escape room "The Agency" by Get a Clue Games in Baltimore
room_address: 8019 Corporate Dr Suite J Nottingham, MD 21236
room_description:
The Agency was attacked! In a matter of minutes, someone breached security, managed to capture a senior agent and make it out of the building without getting caught. While nothing from the Research Division has been stolen, the agent was kidnapped from the most secure facility in the world.
Everyone is on red alert. Teams are already scrambling. Your team's mission is to find clues to rescue the missing agent, find out why The Agency was attacked and put a stop to it! The best place to start is where everything unfolded, his office.
